com.bbn.openmap.layer.link
Interface LinkConstants

All Known Implementing Classes:
ClientLink, Link, LinkGraphic
public interface LinkConstants

The LinkConstants object is an interface that describes all the constants that relate directly to the Link object, and that are defined by the Link Protocol. They are kept here in the LinkContants interface to keep the Link object less cluttered.
